{
  "stem": "18068.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 170.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the highest degree in the nursing service in the army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] if you had the stripes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This is a higher degree.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You're trained as a medical nursing,",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you passed the exams and you got--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't go higher.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where did you do the training?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did they-- did you stay in London or did they--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A place in Kent called Sittingbourne, Kent, near Chatham.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there we were shifted up to Scotland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did all our training up in Scotland, because it's rough there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hills, lakes, and so on, because we were in the casualty service with the infantry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to do the same work, same training as infantry, but we weren't allowed to hold a gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were protected by the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were never allowed to hold a gun, any rifle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we did the same training, but without arms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Full uniform.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whereabouts in Scotland were you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the south up to Edinburgh, Glasgow, Inverness, right up north.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then when the-- when the invasion was there, we were shifted over to the west coast.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Argyllshire, which is rugged and not many people there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Civilians weren't allowed [? for ?] that part, and there we had to do our training, invasion training.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Landings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, going through the water fully clothed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doing training in water, climbing up mountains, which is-- Scotland has.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the whole idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were shifted to the west coast, which is quiet [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there we were there until the invasion started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my unit, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm coming to that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the [? thoughts ?] were good, except one.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
